    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows 2 people throwing a ball back and forth. Person A stands on the left side of the figure and throws the ball overhead to the right toward person B on the right side of the figure who runs towards the left.\" src=\"/images/87429aaed8405fff16e521d7f7f3b4f5.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two people are throwing a ball back and forth. At the instant shown in the figure, Person <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>A</mtext></math></span></span> is not moving relative to the ground, the ball is moving horizontally to the right, and Person <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>B</mtext></math></span></span> is running to the left. Which of the following claims about the kinetic energy of the ball is correct?</p>\n",
